<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white pt-32 pb-20 px-4 relative overflow-hidden">
    
    <!-- Decorative Background Element -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full max-w-4xl h-full pointer-events-none opacity-20">
        <div class="w-full h-[500px] bg-gradient-to-b from-[#D4AF37] to-transparent rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-[#D4AF37] mb-6 brand-font tracking-tighter uppercase">The Platform</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Directives for a sovereign future. We advocate for the structural evolution of the human experience through logic, machine context, and biological integrity.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Agenda Grid -->
        <div class="space-y-8">

            <!-- 1. Modernizing Justice -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-[#D4AF37] hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                    <div class="bg-[#D4AF37]/10 p-4 rounded-full text-[#D4AF37]">
                        <i class="fas fa-balance-scale-right text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 brand-font">Modernizing Justice</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            Moving beyond retributive antiquity. We advocate for a justice system built on data-driven restoration and objective truth, removing the "illusory hierarchy" of bias in favor of equitable, high-resolution legal frameworks.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 2. Biological Fidelity -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-[#20B2AA] hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                    <div class="bg-[#20B2AA]/10 p-4 rounded-full text-[#20B2AA]">
                        <i class="fas fa-dna text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 brand-font">Biological Fidelity</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            The elimination of substance poisoning. True freedom requires a clear signal. We stand for the removal of environmental and systemic toxins that compromise human biology, ensuring the vessel is as pure as the intent.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 3. Machine Context & Conflict Intervention -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-[#F4C430] hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                    <div class="bg-[#F4C430]/10 p-4 rounded-full text-[#F4C430]">
                        <i class="fas fa-microchip text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 brand-font">Machine Context</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            Expansion of machine-mediated social conflict. We leverage artificial intelligence not just for art, but as a neutral arbiter in human friction—providing context where there is noise and intervention where there is irrationality.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 4. Neural Maximization -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-[#FF4500] hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                    <div class="bg-[#FF4500]/10 p-4 rounded-full text-[#FF4500]">
                        <i class="fas fa-brain text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 brand-font">Maximizing Neural Outcomes</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            Every human brain deserves its highest potential. We advocate for infrastructure that optimizes cognitive health, learning, and neural plasticity, making "superpowers" an baseline accessible to every individual regardless of origin.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 5. Eliminating Addiction-Based Capitalism -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-[#9370DB] hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                    <div class="bg-[#9370DB]/10 p-4 rounded-full text-[#9370DB]">
                        <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 brand-font">Post-Addiction Economics</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            Ending the exploitation of the dopamine loop. We seek to reform markets that profit from dependency, pivoting toward a value-based economy that rewards growth rather than the maintenance of addiction.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 6. Dialogue Towards Utopia -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-[#FFD700] hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                    <div class="bg-[#FFD700]/10 p-4 rounded-full text-[#FFD700]">
                        <i class="fas fa-comments text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 brand-font">Constructive Utopianism</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            Dialogue is the bridge. We foster a culture of constructive interaction aimed at the "endgame"—a society where technology and human spirit converge into a functional, sustainable utopia.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- 7. Structural & Cultural Reform -->
            <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-10 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-[#FFFFFF] hover:bg-white/5 transition-all duration-300">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start">
                    <div class="bg-white/10 p-4 rounded-full text-white">
                        <i class="fas fa-landmark text-3xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3 brand-font">Governmental Evolution</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                            Reforming the foundation. We demand cultural and governmental shifts that reflect these pillars, transitioning from legacy control systems to modern, transparent, and biologically-aware governance.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <div class="mt-20 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-2xl text-white font-bold mb-6">Align with the Movement</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn-gold px-8 py-4 rounded text-lg shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(212,175,55,0.3)]">
                    Join the Mission
                </a>
                <a href="/merch" class="btn-outline px-8 py-4 rounded text-lg">
                    Represent the Platform
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>